description: WELL APPOINTED EASTSIDE 2 BEDROOM 2.5 BATH WITH TWO DEEDED PARKING SPACES! THIS CLASSICALLY RENOVATED HOME OFFERS OPEN LIVING CONCEPT INCLUDING STAINLESS/GRANITE KITCHEN WITH 6 BURNER STOVE AND LARGE FLOATING ISLAND, DESIGNATED DINING, AND LARGE LIVING AREA WITH GAS FIREPLACE AND CUSTOM BUILT-INS. KINGSIZED PRIMARY WITH LARGE WALK IN CLOSET AND MARBLE BATH INCLUDING DOUBLE VANITY, GLASS ENCLOSED SHOWER AND SOAKING TUB. THE KING SIZED GUEST SUITE IS PERFECTLY SITUATED OFF THE FOYER, OFFERING SECLUSION AND PRIVACY AND COMPLETE WITH STONE AND POLISHED FITTINGS. ADDITIONAL FEATURES INCLUDE CENTRAL AIR, IN UNIT LAUNDRY, GORGEOUS WALNUT HARDWOOD FLOORS, AUDIO PACKAGE, OVERSIZED WINDOWS WITH CUSTOM WINDOW TREATMENTS, AND EXCELLENT STORAGE. THIS UNIQUE UPPER DUPLEX OFFERS PRIVATE ENTRANCE, DEEDED PATIO, A PET FRIENDLY POLICY AND PROFESSIONAL MANAGEMENT.
